import React, { useCallback, useState } from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import { useRouter } from 'next/router'
import { Form, Input, Button, Checkbox } from 'antd'
// import { Button, Input } from '@UI/Atoms'
import { PostType } from '@API/REST'

// const Form = styled.div``
const Inputs = styled.div``
const Actions = styled.div``
interface PropsType {
	onSubmit: (data: PostType) => void
}
export const CreatePostForm: React.FC<PropsType> = ({ onSubmit }): React.ReactElement => {
	const onCancel = useCallback(() => {
		history.back()
	}, [])
	return (
		<Form name='post' initialValues={{ title: '', body: '' }} onFinish={onSubmit}>
			<Form.Item
				label='Title'
				name='title'
				rules={[{ required: true, message: 'Please enter title of post!' }]}
			>
				<Input />
			</Form.Item>
			<Form.Item
				label='Body'
				name='body'
				rules={[{ required: true, message: 'Please enter body of post!' }]}
			>
				<Input.Password />
			</Form.Item>
			<Button type='primary' htmlType='submit'>
				Create
			</Button>
			<Button type='primary' onClick={onCancel}>
				Cancel
			</Button>
		</Form>
	)
}
